Beastkin Realms of Aetheria
The Beastkin primarily inhabit the continent of Pangara, a vast, wild landmass roughly the size of Africa + South America. It lies southeast of Veloria, separated by the Tempest Strait. Pangara is a continent of extreme biodiversity and primal power — endless savannahs, dense jungles, towering highlands, and monster-haunted wilds.
Total Beastkin population: ≈ 92 million (by far the highest population density among the non-human races, thanks to shorter lifespans and high birth rates).
Beastkin society is organized into 8 Major Sovereign Tribal Confederations. These are not traditional kingdoms but powerful alliances of clans bound by blood, totem, and shared territory. They frequently fight among themselves, but most maintain a wary unity against demonic threats.

